relation: Darrow2 - #63 Down, but not out quite yet, Everdred relays his tale to Ness and for the first time brings out the truth of the Mani Mani's power.
Darrow2 - #64 With his final words, Everdred heads off for parts unknown. Meanwhile, Jeff finally enters the cafe and meets up with an old friend. ...Wait, Mockswell? Okay, so maybe not.
Darrow2 - #65 As odd as the cafe is, things are about to get even more strange. The discovery made behind the counter leads to something as dangerous as it is confusing.
Darrow2 - #66 A strange world awaits Jeff and Ness as they finally arrive in Moonside. Unfortunately for them, somebody turned the insanity volume up way too high in this place.
Darrow2 - #67 Stepping into Moonside, Jeff comes to realize that he picked the wrong point in the story to take the lead.
